<p><a name="Theatre" id="Theatre"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Orientalism&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Theatre">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Theatre</span></h4>
<ul>
